Description_lang: Thaelin has found an additional Titan Energy Core to power up another waygate in the Dragon Isles.

description_blz.en_US: Thaelin has found an additional Titan Energy Core to power up another waygate in the Dragon Isles.
description_blz.es_MX: Thaelin ha encontrado otro núcleo de energía titánica para encender otro portal en las Islas Dragón.
description_blz.pt_BR: Thaelin encontrou mais um Núcleo de Energia Titânico para energizar outro pórtico das Ilhas do Dragão.
description_blz.de_DE: Thaelin hat einen zusätzlichen titanischen Energiekern gefunden, der ein weiteres Portal auf den Dracheninseln mit Energie versorgen kann.
description_blz.en_GB: Thaelin has found an additional Titan Energy Core to power up another waygate in the Dragon Isles.

description_blz.ko_KR: 테일린이 또 다른 용의 섬 차원문을 가동하는 데 필요한 티탄 마력 핵을 추가로 발견했습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 塞林發現額外的泰坦能量核心，可為巨龍群島的其他傳送門提供能量。
description_blz.zh_CN: 塞林又找到一个泰坦能量核心来为另一个巨龙群岛界门供能。
